@startuml
title Arquitetura Física do Sistema (Docker + Spring + PostgreSQL)

node "Máquina / Host" {
  
  node "Container Docker: Front-End" {
    artifact "Nginx (opcional) \nArquivos estáticos: HTML/CSS/JS" as Front
  }

  node "Container Docker: Back-End" {
    artifact "Spring Boot App\n(JAR via Maven)" as Backend
  }

  node "Container Docker: PostgreSQL" {
    database "PostgreSQL DB" as Database
  }
}

Front --> Backend : HTTP (REST)
Backend --> Database : JDBC (Port 5432)
@enduml
